  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You quickly morph your body into smoke to avoid being struck by an enemy's assault. Increase your AC by +5 for the triggering attack, and for every other attack you are targeted with, you reduce the attack roll by a 1d4 potentially causing the attack to miss you. For each attack that misses you as a result of this jutsu you may move to a space within 10 feet of you as a gust of smoke. This does not provoke attacks of opportunity.</p><p>If you are currently receiving the benefits of the Smoke Form hijutsu, you can instead move up to 15 feet when an attack misses you as a result of this jutsu, and reduce consecutive attack rolls by 1d6+1.</p>",
